{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"gauzy-golly-sty","description":"## What\nThe snapshot PRIMITIVE (materialize/cache/janitor/gate-source/coherence) is tested against ad-hoc non-rebar tmp git repos, but the end-to-end LLM gate against a non-rebar repo uses only FakeRunner; the live dogfooding ran against rebar itself. No live (real-agent) attested gate run against a generic non-rebar repo.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] A live (or recorded) attested gate run (verify_completion or review_ticket) against a small non-rebar sample repo, asserting it reads the snapshot and produces a signed verdict.\n- [ ] Confirms the process has no rebar-specific assumptions (paths, structure).","id":"efd0-2553-1a0e-456a","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Live end-to-end gate test against a non-rebar sample repo"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782560955068963001,"uuid":"da5b22ab-adf6-4eae-91d1-c7c75b0b6e31"}